@page "/Contact"
@inherits ContactBase

<div class="container mt-4" style="width: 90%">
    <div class="row text-center">
        <h1 class="fs-1 fw-bolder">@Localizer["聯絡我們"]</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 row">
        <h2 class="fs-3 fw-bolder text-success">@Localizer["公司位置"]</h2>
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2155.1695193314977!2d120.91135003960099!3d24.7080378757188!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x34684c9fcd74dc01%3A0x2e4c10450bc733c!2z6Im-5qC855Sf56eR5oqA!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2stw!4v1697684675448!5m2!1szh-TW!2stw" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 row">
        <div class="col-lg">
            <h2 class="fs-3 fw-bolder text-success">@Localizer["聯絡表單"]</h2>
            <div class="pe-5">
                <p class="m-0 indent-2 ">
                    感謝您光臨艾格生科技股份有限公司網站，您的寶貴意見讓我們持續成長。誠摯的歡迎您來信或來電洽詢相關業務，我們將盡快提供您完整的服務，謝謝。
                </p>
                <div class="row pt-2">
                    <div class="col-lg">
                        <p class="m-0">姓名</p>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg">
                        <p class="m-0">Email</p>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row pt-2">
                    <div class="col-lg">
                        <p class="m-0">連絡電話</p>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg">
                        <p class="m-0">主旨</p>
                        <select class="form-select">
                            <option>產品問題</option>
                            <option>技術問題</option>
                            <option>行政問題</option>
                            <option>其他問題</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row pt-2">
                    <div class="col-lg">
                        <p class="m-0">內容</p>
                        <textarea type="text" class="form-control" style="height: 10em;" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row pt-2">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
                        <input type="button" class="form-control" style="width: max-content" value="送出" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg ps-3">
            <h2 class="fs-3 fw-bolder text-success">@Localizer["聯絡資訊"]</h2>
            <p class="m-0 fs-5 text-success">艾格生科技股份有限公司</p>
            <p class="mt-2 mb-1">350401新竹科學園區苗栗縣竹南鎮科北一路21號3樓</p>
            <p class="my-1">電話：037-580079</p>
            <p class="my-1">傳真：037-580393</p>
            <p class="my-1">統一編號：28114813</p>
            <p class="my-1">
                電子郵件：<a href="mailto:xservice@xsensetw.com">xservice@xsensetw.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>


</div>